<br>
((I do not know you, but I feel your plight.  Bane of Innoruuk is a small guild of honorable followers of light, that is less than two months old.  We are having lots of fun, but keeping critical mass can be difficult.  We have recently been debating a guild merger or an alliance.<br>
<br>
We are RP-preferred, have about a dozen active members, consisting of frogloks, a couple of wood elves, a high elf, and a dwarf; we are all low to mid-level, most are in the teens or 20s with our highest members being 30ish at the moment.  We are followers of Mithaniel Marr, his sister Erollisi and Tunare, but we are open to anyone who is allied against Innoruuk.  This does of course, generally rule out followers of Cazic-Thule and Rallos-Zek...  We do not consort with Tier'Dal or their pawns the trolls...<br>
<br>
Stop by our tavern, and check us out!  We may be a good fit for you...<br>
